content.detailedDescription: I was looking out our 2nd story window facing west because my brother pointed out a bird fighting a hawk in the sky,after 30 seconds or so of watching the bird and the hawk , i noticed this cigar shaped object with no wings making no noise what so ever as you hear normally, it came from north east heading west towards the ocean, a few seconds into spotting the object, i then yelled for my brother to come to the window who was only inches behind me since he was also looking at the birds but had just stepped away as i stayed at the window looking up,the object was moving at a high rate of speed for something so oddly shaped traveling in a straight line, we both now we're looking at the object asking each other "where are the wings!?" "what the heck is that!?" "there's no wings dude!" "dude"!? as it travelled west it went into the marine layer and it faded away as it went further west,from the time i spotted it with my eyes to the time i called my brother over to look, it was a good 9 seconds of visual contact with this object.
content.summary: Long white cigar shape with dark depressed lines.

content.detailedDescription:
After a strange dream, i woke up and i felt like if i went outside i might see a ufo.  after getting outside, i didn't see any besides a bright star-like object that looked like it might be venus.  this is the object that i took pictures of and reported.  it didn't look like it was moving at all to me, but i thought i would take pictures anyway, and see what showed up.

because the pictures show other stars as stationary and not blurry, and the object is moving and apparently leaving trails, i thought i would file a report anyway.
content.summary: Went outside and photographed what i thought might have been venus

content.detailedDescription: I was driving back from my friends house in isom, kentucky. it was roughly 1 am, and i had the music on just driving. while going through dry fork (a small community, not quite a town, outside of whitesburg), i noticed what appeared to be a human like creature. they were staggering & falling into the road.. at first i thought this was a very intoxicated human, but when i took a second glance, i discovered otherwise.. i realized that not only was there one of these creatures, but there were 3 of them. they were orange creatures who had huge circle heads.. they were staggering, like i said, so i assume that they may be a crossover between a creature that runs/walks, and crawls.. while driving and seeing them stagger, my initial thought was that they were coming towards my car, so i swerved into the passing lane.  after seeing this, i drove as fast as i could to one of my friends and picked them up... when we got back, the creatures were gone. this sighting really messed with my mind... since then, i've had thoughts of this creature, and i can't help but wonder what these things are. i have not told anyone besides the friend i picked up that night, due to the fact that i know some people would not believe.. it was the most real and true experience i have ever encountered in my life.
content.summary: Creatures with big orange heads falling into the road in eastern kentucky

content.detailedDescription: Witness was out walking his dog when he first noticed a bright light at about 140 degrees. he describes the object as a light on a faint green-blue metallic object. as he observed the object it seemed to turn toward him and approach closer, taking a curved path in a southwesterly direction. when in the original position the object appeared to be the shape of the side of an oval, with a green cast near the top and a light blue cast closer to the bottom. when moving positions and fully facing him, the object appeared to be circular  in shape with a total of 4 lights, two stacked on top of another two, forming a square pattern on a round background. the witness observed the object for between 5 and 10 seconds. the object never made a sound. but it seemed under intelligent control and, as the object turned toward the witness, he had an impression that the object was aware of his presence and that is why it turned. the original size was estimated to be about the size of a half dollar and after approaching him, appeared to be the size of a tennis ball or baseball. after observing the object move toward him, the witness said the light just blinked out and he did not see it again.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Bright object first observed at angle then straight on with 4 lights stacked in pairs

content.detailedDescription: Well i was going through my phone pictures and found a video and picture i have no memory of. in the video i say i see it but don't know if i can get a picture. i say not good and then it cuts off. the picture is what looks like a bright light sitting on the grown and there are these weid lines or waves in front of it. truely i'm not sure what i saw, where i saw it or for how long . did i see something you tell me i know i hear myself get out of the car that is very weid and to have no memory of it at all is spooky!
content.summary: Unknown just found video and picture no memory of eventi

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to work north on semoran blvd around 6:00-6:05am when i noticed what i first thought to be a low flying plane heading to orlando international airport (a few miles south) from my driver side window. what made me look closer was how low and big it was, first thing i did was to roll down the window and look for a fuselage, but there was none. it was a big triangle object (150-200 feet wide and 20-25 feet high) and it was stationary hoovering above the residential neighborhood east of semoran boulevard (between curry ford rd and lake underhill dr). the object had rounded edges and bright white lights at each corner, just before i lost it out of sight there was a fourth white light coming on from the center of the object. it was very low and very close, i would say 50 feet above the ground and no more than 1/4mile from where i was. the trees and 2 story buildings across the street were tall enough to block my view. i made a u turn at the traffic light on semoran and lake underhill and got my camera ready but the light took forever and the object was gone by the time. i've never reported or had something to report before, but i'm really interested to see if anyone else saw or reported this. there is no way i'm the only one i saw it as it was in the middle of the city and it was big.
content.summary: Huge rectangular object, hoovering above a residential neighborhood

content.detailedDescription: At 10:45pm i took my dogs outside. i first notice the object when there was a bright flash of white light in the lower part of the northern sky. i thought it was a falling star because of the brightness of it. by the third flash i could definitely tell it was not a plane and moving unpredictably. i felt like this is amazing i'm really seeing another ufo. (my first was in 2007 and i filled out this form.) i started counting 5 to 15 seconds in between flashes. then i ran inside to get my phone for the camera. of course it was gone when i got back outside. but i started recording video anyways. i saw a falling star and a satellite. then i saw a plane just above the houses and not far away. it was flying north to south with a white light directly in front of it that was not flashing and keeping pace with it. this goes on for about three seconds. then the light jumps very quickly to the back of the plane and keeps pace for another three seconds. then the light moves to the north at the same altitude and about the with of my hand away from the plane. it then hoovers in place for about ten minutes. at this point it looks like a big star putting out a constant white and red flickering of light. i lost sight of it when i was scanning the sky for a few seconds. about fifteen minutes later i'm still looking around and see two plane flying low coming from the south going north. they fly right where the ufo was and keep going north. then about thirty seconds later two more low flying plane are following behind the first two. then a cop drives by real slow. the cop was probably a coincidence.
content.summary: Flashed on and off for a few minutes in different parts of the sky. then flew circles around a plane, then hovered.

content.detailedDescription: My husband and i were driving to the dfw (dallas-fort worth) area from lubbock last wednesday/thursday. out of complete darkness in the sky a line of bright white lights appears in front of our car. dome shaped,  flashing lights in a repetitive pattern, all white. the craft would disappear then reappear in different spots. seen over highway 84 heading southeast of hermleigh, and over i-20 eastbound coming into sweetwater. we stopped on i-20 to take pics, it flew right over us. the underside had 3 white lights in a triangle shape. low humming sound, no air moving. my husband took all the pics, he is/was skeptical about ufo sightings. he is not anymore. we have more than 5 pics if anyone wants/needs to see more. this took place between hermleigh and sweetwater, tx. it faded out to total darkness just before we got near sweetwater exits off the interstate. our phones kept running out of charge while this object was near and the bluetooth in my car kept re-syncing while the craft flew over us.
content.summary: White lights on a disk shaped object that would appear then disappear then reappear once it flew directly over our head it was actually triangle shaped and had three bottom lights in a triangle pattern but appeared as a sphere when it was not directly ove

content.detailedDescription: On april 17th of 2016 i was out in my backyard having a cigarette (i need to quit i know) when i spotted what it appeared to be a "fireball" crossing the sky coming from the west, it was straight ahead from me and was about a few miles up from my neighbor's home and our divider tree line and heading east according to my iphone compass. started taking pics with my cell phone, zooming in and out on the ufo as it went by, the sun went over the horizon around 8:40pm when i saw it. it was a crystal clear day and afternoon and sun was reaching the horizon and airplanes were all over the place as usual. within 10 minutes and already dark it crossed the sky again in same fashion, from same origin point and direction/trajectory but i did not see it making a "u-turn" the first time so i am guessing there were 2 of these flying in same path. i stayed out super intrigued after the first ufo appeared and had noted the area when it became visible to the eye just above one of the yard's pine trees. i continued looking at the night sky, planes flying by with their beacons, a few stars showing up and then it showed up in the distance, same origin point and within 15 minutes from the first sight. i saw a lit dot except that this time it appeared as if it left something behind or departed from it, something stationary so i continued taking pictures with my cell phone as it went by in the night, same heading as previous ufo. started as a light at a distance flying fast with no sound whatsoever then it somehow transformed itself into a moving fireball/cloud with random whites and reds then it disappeared, it went dark and stealth. i must have taken like 100 pictures, some show things that i cant explain, others are just pics of a clear night sky. whatever this was, it was fast, silent and had the capability to somehow camouflage itself in a cloud form. i did not have a computer which is why i couldn't report it at the time. i used my iphone "skills" zooming in and out and using editing options to clear the images. i freaked out a bit when i zoomed-in some of the pics and added a bit of brightness, contrast, and even used the red eye as i was running out of options in the phone, i tried it all several times and it finally revealed itself, whatever it was. you all take a look at the pictures and you tell me what you see. i have witnessed a few ufo's in my past including a not so long ago sight also reported here but i have never seeing a ufo as if it came out of a box, a window-box-like just hanging up there in the sky, this "box" resembles the microsoft window in lock-screen in most computers. i could've swear this second ufo came out of the "window box" which i didn't notice at first but then pictures revealed it. could this be a portal window/door to enter the earth atmosphere unnoticed? i can only upload 10 pics so. *in the picture where the ufo is surrounded by what it looks like a red transparent set of flower petals (red cloud form) looking like a fireball from a distance, the ufo can be seen to have a double arrow-end body shape with some x's configuration in the middle, i was able to see through the red cloud by using the red eye feature in my iphone. - it resembles the same ufo shape that a tourist recorded from the empire state in nyc in april 2 of 2016, posted in the ufosightingsdaily site.
content.summary: Fireball/cloud ufo came out of window/cube in the sky

content.detailedDescription: My mother and i were visiting at her house in south houston a week ago. we're avid sky watchers looking for fast walkers and anything out of the normal. we've seen many strange things in the past but i've seen more than she has. i told her about an indecent before where i saw two "worm hole" looking clouds above my old house near the beach where i couldn't see any objects creating the ever lengthening formations that had the ends expanding. the night last week we were watching proved i wasn't crazy. i watched the same formation streak slowly across the night sky around 2200 hours moving from an orbital enter position to a linear south east direction. i pointed it out and shouted "that's the thing i saw before!" and she ran inside to grab binoculars because there was no visible object in the front of the "cloud". upon tracking the black cloud i was able to observe the object which she found also. it was moving slowly in a straight line and began to slow down. the streak it was leaving began to retract slightly like it was leaving and while we watched the object we both lost sight of it suddenly. after regaining sight of it we had noticed it had drastically changed direction and was headed more south but in an upward direction. i've posted things before to mufon in the past describing my abduction case when i was really young in which i was left with an implant in my lip but o never heard anything back, but after this incident last week i just noticed that the object in my lip has suddenly vanished leaving that part of my lip feeling slightly... hollow?? i don't know how to say it. but now, since the last sighting i've suffered from nightmares and a headache that won't go away no matter what i do!! i'm not afraid of our intergalactic brothers, i just want someone to believe me! they've been with me since i was young   and was always ok with everything but this last time something has left me in pain. did a new species get ahold of me? something more malicious? and why won't mufon investigate? i was contacted once and the investigator vanished? what's going on? why am i afraid now? i loved my friends from before but now... something is different. that worm hole brought in something else. i'm sure of it.
content.summary: Linear black cloud at night with no visible cause until viewed under binoculars then object quickly changed direction

content.detailedDescription:
At approximately 08:20hrs pst on may 02,2016
i was driving westward through walnut grove.  i saw two objects hovering in the sky ahead. they were remaining in a stationary position for at least a few minutes.  i managed to get one picture while i drove. there was no where where i could pull over to take another picture.  i was coming up to some trees which blocked my view. but, i thought that when i got through the trees and get to the clearing i would pull over for some more shots.  when i got to the clearing.... there was nothing to be seen in the skies above any longer... what ever it was had disappeared on me.
my location was 88th avenue and 212th street looking west towards fort langley bc.
content.summary: I saw 2 objects reflecting in the sun while i was driving; they were stationary.

content.detailedDescription: Saw lights last night went out with phone to capture pictures and by golly they were there again so i got pictures and videos

content.detailedDescription:
I was feeding horses and had just shut a 12 foot gate, turned to the north and off to my right15 degrees at alt 40 degrees saw a white object, but heard a jet also moving much slower but never saw it as i was locked on to the silver object. 

the sun was the key to me even being able to see it, the sun was 6:30 evening low in the south west but still high enough, the object that small and moving fast, it was out of sight in two minutes or less, in any other situation would not have been visible for me to lock onto so easily. i don't think this was of this world. too small and too fast. i don't think it was all that far away .. one mile as it came by me and then off into the west at great speed straight line .. and as it sped away the jet sound was still close by and going overhead much farther away and crawling compared to this "thing".

when i first saw it and white i was thinking an air born white grocery sack.

lost track when it got about 15 to 20 miles away .. gone.

very small, round, white to silver, moving easily at one thousand miles per hour but no sonic booms and no noise. not of this world.
content.summary: Thought i heard a jet going to mnt. home air base but saw small silverish round ball, small, moving at an incredible speed .. 1-2,000 mph

content.detailedDescription: On may1st,2016 approximately 8:00 pm i was sitting on the front porch with my wife. i then noticed a bright object streaking across the sky at a downward sloped trajectory towards the east. i walked out into the yard to get a better view of the object.I only ended up getting 1 picture of the object on my phone. approximately 20 to 30 minutes later 2 planes fly over my house heading in the same direction the object was heading. i didn't manage to get a picture of the planes though. i couldn't tell how big the 1st plane was, but the 2nd plane was really big with 3 flashing lights on the back with the red light located in the middle of the other 2 lights. it looked like a plane that could carry a big cargo. (note: i'm not an expert on planes, ufo's, asteroids, meteorites, or comets.)
content.summary: Was sitting on the front porch when i seen something bright steaking across the sky so i took a picture.

content.detailedDescription: Parked, taking pictures of sunset through opened car window. when looking at pictures once we were home, we noticed the object.  the photos were taken with a second of each other but the object had moved significantly. pilot friend said it could have been a drone but he wasn't sure. a friend suggested i post it here.
content.summary: Green, quickly moving object heading north, west of eureka, ca, over pacific ocean at sunset.

content.detailedDescription: Witnessed three of these object in various positions in sky they seemed to be hovering in three different positions one directly west of me one southwest another hovering towards the other two in west direction they were verticle shape in the sky not horizontal the strange thing is there was also a meteorite that fell between these objects lit up the sky and then disapated amazing sight i witnessed for about 15 minutes tonight i will be out there with camera hopefully it shows up and my phone will be able to see them.
content.summary: Witnessed three of these object in various positions in sky

content.detailedDescription: I live in las vegas nevada towards the west side of the valley. on or about the evening of april 14 2016 at about 8 pm i stepped out onto my backyard patio to enjoy the clear night sky. i noticed a spotlight shining into the sky towards the west. i figured it was at the red rock casino to mark its anniversary. as i looked at the spotlight moving through the sky i noticed a very bright reflection of something in the sky also towards the west. it was about 45 degrees up from the horizon. at first my thoughts were that it was an airplane, but there were no navigation lights at all. then i thought it could be a satellite, but it was moving way too slow and the reflection emitted was tremendously bright, square in shape, very large in size, and appeared to be caused by rotation of the object. i then thought it could be the space station, but i have seen that many times and it never appeared to look like the light i was seeing. definitely not a planet, nor the moon either. the object was moving in a straight line from west to east and very, very slowly. at times the reflection would be intensely bright for a couple of seconds then dim to darkness and many seconds later be intensely bright again. this pattern repeated itself for the entire time i watched as it slowly traveled to the east where i lost sight of it behind my neighbors tree line.The size of the reflection was that of a bb or pellet held at arms length. the reflection seemed to be very high in altitude. there were airliners in night sky and they moved quickly in and out of view. the light i saw was visible to me for about 15 minutes. i was totally mesmerized by what i saw. i suppose i can explain it away as the spotlight shining on something traveling high in the atmosphere, but i would like to know if other people saw this as well. i have never seen anything move that slowly through the sky and exhibit such a bright light whether emitted or reflected. its been in my thoughts ever since. thnx for any info u may be able to provide regarding my sighting.
content.summary: I witnessed a very slow moving object at night very high in sky with a very bright reflective surface.

content.detailedDescription: N/a
content.summary: Blinking lights hovering

content.detailedDescription:
East of westerville, ohio

sept. 14, 2015 - 10:05p est, i observed the same bright light approaching from the north, that i had seen just a few nights prior, and i had no camera with me!  the craft entered my frame of vision from the west (skimming tree tops), turned 90 degrees (on a dime), and the craft was moving directly at me.  the navigational lights were that of a jet, but the headlight was 10x brighter than a typical jet headlight.  i had just taken my camera in from my night of sky gazing, took the dog out, took her back in, and started to lock up the door for the night when i got a ‘psychic’ message to return outside and to stand by a particular tree, which i did.  very strange!  sure as the devil, that’s when i spotted the craft approaching from the west and just north of me.  i backed away from the tree and boldly stood as the craft centered directly between my eyes and came overhead at an est. 15 – 20 mph. or less.  it presented what appeared to be a full display of lights, including a ring of brilliant red individual lights, dead center in the belly of the craft.  it was lit like ‘times square’ and utterly silent.  another triangle, but this time, just over my head!  this time, left light red and right, green; different from prior, higher slightly higher altitude sightings of 2 triangles together, with red and white lights, only, from days earlier.  the head-beam was brighter than the moon, and cast for a couple miles forward, at least, and came over at an est. 100 feet – 125 feet at best.  it was very low and slow.  i know i said 15 – 20 mph. but in reality it may have moving at 5 mph. for all i know.  i was hypnotized by the green light and a feeling of peace and love came over me.  again … very strange!  ‘they’ (whoever or whatever they are) allowed me to see the entire craft.  i was in absolute awe! and … i wasn’t the least bit frightened!  i know the light mesmerized me as i stood smiling at the craft approaching me!  if it were any lower, i could have hit it with a rock.  as it passed overhead, i was dead center with the brilliant red belly lights.  if they wanted to abduct me, they would have!  as it was about to exit our property, the only sound it made was a low crackling sound.  the back edge was trimmed with yellow-orange oblong ports.  i got a great look at the craft, but missed a sensational photo op!  this struck me as a total anti-gravity craft, as the giant equilateral triangle barely moved through the air, with no wind or air disturbance being generated whatsoever.
content.summary: Close encounter with large triangle ufo - slow approach and directed itself directly over me.  the communicated via telepathy to get me outside.  i was done for the night.

content.detailedDescription: I was watching the international space station live feed and noticed bright light that was well above the horizon and appeared for about 30 seconds and faded out. i am unsure if it's just reflection off of the lense from the sun, but appeared similar to what was witnessed april 5 2016 from the iss feed. i took 3 screen shots , one just before i saw it as the iss was coming into the light after being on the darkside, another as it appeared for about 15 seconds and the third as it began to dim or fade off. the object or light i am referring to is at the left portion of the shot
content.summary: Watching iss at 1:37 pst. witnessed light above the horizon as it was transferring from the darkside of the planet to the light

content.detailedDescription: After hitting a tumbleweed driving at 95 mph on a slimy wet asphalt road, a section of i-80 in utah not far from the nevada border, my car started spinning and sliding, changing direction twice, first to get out of the way of a speeding big rig, and then not to slide off the road and start rolling which would have surely been fatal not having my seat belt on. most of the sliding happened with my car being backward. i was in shock, my hands frozen to the steering wheel, surely not having any control over the vehicle. the behavior of my car was so unreal, i could find no other explanation than a tractor-beam controlling it from above.
content.summary: As described in black jack: a day in the afterlife, downloadable from amazon

content.detailedDescription:
I was at home, lying on my bed at 10:50 in the evening. the room was completely dark, and after a few minutes my eye was drawn to an usually bright star-like object outside my bedroom window. it is not usual to see a few dim stars outside my window (the city lights drown out most of them) but this one was unusually vibrant. 
 
after watching the star for less than a minute, the object seemed to move westward very quickly, only to stop and hover again. i began to watch it more closely, and it seemed to actively move fluidly back and forth across the sky, two or three times a minute. each time it would stop and hover once again. it was a cloudless night, and although i regularly see planes and helicopters in my neighbourhood, this made no sound and had no navigation lights.

i immediately grabbed my phone (the only camera within reach), and managed to take photos and take a short video. while doing both, i made sure to rest my hands on the window ledge, and brace my arms to reduce any hand movement. in the video the object can be seen repeatedly moving. in the photos, the object seems to routinely change shape, beginning as a glowing orb, then seeming to 'burst', with a clear hole in the middle, and reforming into a circular orb again. it was incredibly unusual. 

the object made me feel both curious and unnerved, as although it was star-like, it didn't seem natural somehow. the object behaved oddly. although i didn't feel unsafe, i was unnerved, and eventually wanted to stop watching the object. after about 20 minutes, i stopped observing it, although it was still in the sky, but far further west than when i had started watching.

any insight you could give would be greatly appreciated. although i'm aware it very likely could be a natural phenomenon, it seemed unnatural and was unnerving enough that i thought i should report it. thank you!
content.summary: Unusually bright light seemed hovering and moving regularly across sky. seemed to change shape.

content.detailedDescription:
I was outside late at night, laying on my back in the yard, watching netflix on my phone. i was looking upward watching an episode of south park. it caught my eye because it was bright orange and red. i couldn't understand what it was. i kept thinking it had to be a hot air balloon or something. i was seeing it from underneath. it was a bright red circle that looked like fire, due to the way it flickered. that circle was the center of a much larger circle that was a bright orange red. it looked like the center was the fire and the rest of the object was illuminated it. 

i realized it couldnt be a hot air balloon because the basket would hide the fire. i wondered if it could be some weird paper floating fire art, like what you might see in japan, but enormous. there wasn't any noise, which really stuck out to me. i am used to the sound of planes and helicopters. this was not high and climbing altitude like a plane which are noisy. it was lower like a helicopter might be, but without sound and it was enormous by comparison. 

i tried to get out of my netflix and get to my camera on my phone. i stood up and tried to get a better look at it. i never felt like i could get a different view of it. it was moving too slowly, not a dead hover but really slow like a hot air balloon. but it always looked like i was seeing it from underneath. when it moved from over my neighbors house, north, maybe 2 city clocks really slowly, i watched it and there wasn't a side view , it still looked like a glowing orange circle with a bright red circle on the bottom underside.So, disc shaped i suppose because it didn't seem deep from the side but was 3 dimensional and pie shaped.

i couldn't get my phone to work, but did not attribute it to the ship. i was just learning to use the new smart phone. it had to be fairly fast. but it seemed like it lasted to maybe 8 minutes. i gave up on the phone and just wanted to watch it, because it was unlike anything i had ever seen. i really never was in to ufo stuff. i still wish i knew what it was. i kept my eye on it. it moved north a few blocks and then it just disappeared.
